%define;boxchar(x,y)
  %if;(x=1)┼
  %elseif;((x>1 and x<4) or (x>7 and x<16) or (x>31 and x<64) or (x>127 and x<256) or (x>511 and x<1024)or (x>2047 and x<4096))
    %if;(y=0)
      %if;(x%2=0)
        %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)╷%else;┬%end;
      %else;
        %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)╵%else;┴%end;
      %end;
    %else;
       %if;(x%2=0)
         %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)╶%else;├%end;
       %else;
         %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)╴%else;┤%end;
       %end;
    %end;
  %elseif;((x>3 and x<8) or (x>15 and x<32) or (x>63 and x<128) or (x>255 and x<512) or (x>1023 and x<2048) or (x>4095 and x<8192))
    %if;(y=0)

      %else;
        %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)╴%else;┤%end;

    %else;

%end;

%define;graph(xx,yy,zz)
  %let;levelup;%expr(xx+1)%in;
  %let;leveldown;%expr(xx-1)%in;
  %if;(zz=2)
    %foreach;ancestor_level(levelup)
      %foreach;ancestor;
        %if;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v %2 = 0)
          %let;anc_sosahalf;%expr(ancestor.anc_sosa.v/2)%in;
          %let;top;%expr(topxx_yy(anc_sosahalf)*hb)%in;
          %let;left;%expr(leftxx_yy(anc_sosahalf)*wb)%in;
          <tt><a style="%ttstyle;top:%top;px;left:%left;px;" href="%prefix;%ancestor.access;"
          title="[*generation/generations]0 %level; – Sosa %if;(ancestor.interval != "") = Sosa %ancestor.interval;%else;%ancestor.anc_sosa; & %expr(ancestor.anc_sosa+1)%end;&#013;
            %if;(ancestor.is_male) ♂%else; ♀%end; %ancestor; (%ancestor.occ)&#013;
            %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year != "")° %ancestor.birth_date.year;%end;
            %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year != "" and ancestor.is_dead) – %end;
            %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year = "" and ancestor.death_date.year != "")†%else;%ancestor.death_date.year;%end;&#013;
            %if;(not ancestor.has_parents) [*missing parents].&#013;%end;
            %if;(ancestor.spouse.is_male) ♂%else; ♀%end; %ancestor.spouse; (%ancestor.spouse.occ)&#013;
            %if;(ancestor.spouse.birth_date.year != "")° %ancestor.spouse.birth_date.year;%end;
            %if;(ancestor.spouse.birth_date.year != "" and ancestor.spouse.is_dead) – %end;
            %if;(ancestor.spouse.birth_date.year = "" and ancestor.spouse.death_date.year != "")†%else;%ancestor.spouse.death_date.year;%end;&#013;
            %if;(not ancestor.spouse.has_parents) [*missing parents].%end;">
          %if;(ancestor.same != "")╳%else;%apply;boxchar(anc_sosahalf,yy)%end;</a></tt>
        %end;
      %end;
    %end;
    %foreach;ancestor_level(xx)
      %foreach;ancestor;
        %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)
          %let;top4;%expr(topxx_yy(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*hb)%in;
          %let;left4;%expr(leftxx_yy(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*wb)%in;
          <tt><a style="%ttstyle;top:%top4;px;left:%left4;px;" href="%prefix;m=ADD_PAR;ip=%ancestor.index;" 
          title="[*missing sosa] %expr(ancestor.anc_sosa.v*2) & %expr(ancestor.anc_sosa.v*2+1) – [*generation/generations]0 %expr(level+1)&#013;
          [*add] %apply;a_of_b%with;[the parents]%and;Sosa %ancestor.anc_sosa.v;%end; %ancestor;">·</a></tt>
        %end;
      %end;
    %end;
  %else;
    %foreach;ancestor_level(xx)
      %foreach;ancestor;
        %let;top;%expr(topxx_yy(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*hb)%in;
        %let;left;%expr(leftxx_yy(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*wb)%in;
        <tt><a style="%ttstyle;top:%top;px;left:%left;px;" href="%prefix;%ancestor.access;"
        title="Sosa %ancestor.anc_sosa;%if;(ancestor.same != "") = Sosa %ancestor.same;%end; – [*generation/generations]0 %level;&#013;
          %if;(ancestor.is_male) ♂%else; ♀%end; %ancestor; (%ancestor.occ)&#013;
          %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year != "")° %ancestor.birth_date.year;%end;
          %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year != "" and ancestor.is_dead) – %end;
          %if;(ancestor.birth_date.year = "" and ancestor.death_date.year != "")†%else;%ancestor.death_date.year;%end;&#013;
          %if;(not ancestor.has_parents) [*missing parents].%end;">
        %if;(ancestor.same != "")╳%else;%apply;boxchar(ancestor.anc_sosa.v,yy)%end;</a></tt>
      %end;
    %end;
    %foreach;ancestor_level(leveldown)
      %foreach;ancestor;
        %if;(not ancestor.has_parents)
          %let;top2;%expr(topxx_yy(ancestor.anc_sosa.v*2)*hb)%in;

%end;

          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───%else;│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=9 or xx=10)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───────%else;│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=11 or xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───────────────%else;│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v >7 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v < 16)
        %if;(xx=6 or xx=7)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│%else;─%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=8 or xx=9)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│%else;───%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=10 or xx=11)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />%else;───────%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│%else;───────────────%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>15 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<32)
        %if;(xx=7 or xx=8)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)─%else;│%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=9 or xx=10)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───%else;│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=11 or xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───────%else;│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>31 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<64)
        %if;(xx=8 or xx=9)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│%else;─%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=10 or xx=11)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│%else;───%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│<br />│%else;───────%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>63 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<128)
        %if;(xx=9 or xx=10)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)─%else;│%end;</tt>
        %elseif(xx=11 or xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)───%else;│<br />│<br />│%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>127 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<256)
        %if;(xx=10 or xx=11)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│%else;─%end;</tt>
        %elseif;(xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│<br />│<br />│%else;───%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>255 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<512)
        %if;(xx=11 or xx=12)
          <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)─%else;│%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %elseif;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v>511 and ancestor.anc_sosa.v<1024)
        %if;(xx=12)
         <tt style="%ttstyle;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px">%if;(yy=0)│%else;─%end;</tt>
        %end;
      %end;
    %end;
  %end;
%end;

<h3><tt>Sosa I-tree 5</tt></h3>
<div class="menu" style="position:relative;width:120px;height:210px;">
  %foreach;ancestor_level(5)
    %foreach;ancestor;
      %let;top;%expr(top5_0(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*h5)%in;
      %let;left;%expr(10+left5_0(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*w5)%in;
      %let;top_;%expr(top5_0_(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*h5)%in;
      %let;left_;%expr(10+left5_0_(ancestor.anc_sosa.v)*w5)%in;
      %let;bg;%if;(ancestor.same != "")CBFECE;%else;%apply;bg(level)%end;%in;
      <a style="position:absolute;top:%top;px;left:%left;px;background-color:#%bg;;padding:%pad;;font-family:monospace;font-size:%font;"
      href="%prefix;%ancestor.access;"
      title="Sosa %ancestor.anc_sosa;[:] %if;(ancestor.is_male)♂%else;♀%end; %ancestor.first_name; %ancestor.surname; (%ancestor.occ) – [*generation/generations]0 %level;">
      %if;(ancestor.same != "")%ancestor.same;%else;%ancestor.anc_sosa;%end;</a>
      %if;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v=2 or ancestor.anc_sosa.v=3)
         <div style="position:absolute;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px;padding:5px;">↑</div>
      %end;
      %if;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v=3)
         <div style="position:absolute;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px;padding:5px;">↓</div>
      %end;
      %if;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v=4 or ancestor.anc_sosa.v=6)
         <div style="position:absolute;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px;padding:5px;">←</div>
      %end;
      %if;(ancestor.anc_sosa.v=5 or ancestor.anc_sosa.v=7)
         <div style="position:absolute;top:%top_;px;left:%left_;px;padding:5px;">→</div>
      %end;
    %end;
  %end;
</div>
